    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1014949498">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1014949498" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1014949498" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1014949498">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/saintini/">恪彥</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-02-24</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">陈氏寅恪先生尝言：华夏民族之文化，历数千载之演进，造极于赵宋之世。如何在有限的篇章，将如此充满争议，却又引人入胜的“华彩”大时代，寻找到一个面向大众较为恰如其分的纵观横截面，且即不失取学术研究之成果，集大成；又能字字珠玑，值得反复诵读，对宋史研究者来说，自是不易。简而言之，本书可用四字概括，平实中肯。亦或，毕竟余蔚。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1016298522">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1016298522" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1016298522" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1016298522">有用</a>
